Copper River Knowledge System - Java services

This Java/BlazeDS webapp provides services and servlets that are used by
the CRKS Flex client. The Java middleware connects to a backend PostgreSQL
database and GeoServer.

To install:
* Copy src/main/resources/hibernate.cfg.xml.example to src/main/resources/hibernate.cfg.xml
* Edit src/main/resources/hibernate.cfg.xml and update to match deployment:
** hibernate.connection.url
** hibernate.connection.username
** hibernate.connection.password
* Run mvn install
* Copy build.properties.example to build.properties
* Edit build.properties and update properties to match deployment
* Run ant deploy-live (or deploy-test) 